heif.boxes

Class ItemInformationBox.ItemInfoEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • heif.boxes.Box
      • heif.boxes.FullBox
        • heif.boxes.ItemInformationBox.ItemInfoEntry
  • Enclosing class:
    ItemInformationBox

    private static class ItemInformationBox.ItemInfoEntry
extends FullBox
    A nested class used to manage the ItemInfoEntry box. This box type is known as infe as part of the Item Information Box.

      • ItemInfoEntry

        private ItemInfoEntry(Box box,
                      SequentialByteReader reader)
        This constructor creates a derived Box object, providing additional information about selected items. This aids in determining if HEIC image files contain an embedded EXIF directory.
        Parameters:
        box - the super Box object
        reader - a SequentialByteReader object for sequential byte array access
